Typical install notes on different unix systems

Naming convention:

UNAME   = `uname -s`
VERSION = [DISTRO_]
    check /etc/issue or /etc/redhat_version or /etc/debian_version
    check /etc/os-release
    check the command:  hostnamectl
    check the command:  lsb_release -a
    

